{"tid":1678130,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"剛買Surface Go, WINDOWS UPDATE 期間死左","createTime":"2019-10-27T13:23:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T11:24:52.000Z","uid":87535,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b3c3472fb31785215f602376adc7632fc65ded6e","tid":1678130,"uid":87535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T13:23:54.000Z","msg":"昨天買左部SURFACE GO , 8G RAM, 128GB SSD, 買新機返來例牌行WINDOWS UPDATE, 點知行到咁上下, 死機. 好算我黑仔,買到次貨.  今日拿返去間鋪換, 換左返來, 行WINDOWS UPDATE 又死過. 咁大間Microsoft 出產品或者出UPDATE 前有無試清楚架. 我真係對Microsoft 出既硬件無晒信心. BTW, 有無巴打知道點解決宜家既問題?<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yCVcw35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyCVcw35.jpg&h=c5b43582&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86cfc9a283f7be2f333d270a72309ce503857170","tid":1678130,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T13:24:24.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借個位<br />\n鐘庭耀發起全港性民調，追蹤長期民意<br />\n<br />\n連登post: 鍾庭耀教授都企左出來....你仲做冷氣軍師??<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n眾籌link: <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4XlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=c867a9ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"6dc360e0a4dddf836dbeb3d9dbe6a9dba7f8d6d8","tid":1678130,"uid":216354,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T13:35:04.000Z","msg":"surface 垃圾果然名不虛傳"},{"pid":"f4baba2f35de99304925e15d0e1a162fc4a44386","tid":1678130,"uid":28558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T13:45:53.000Z","msg":"連登一眾巴打怒屌你都買"},{"pid":"2cd5153b6d20effa8a38ee1151a0914edd1a687c","tid":1678130,"uid":87535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4baba2f35de99304925e15d0e1a162fc4a44386","tid":1678130,"uid":